Utility Classes and Implementatons:
===================================
Review the utility functions in 'dtg-utils.h' for use in the plugin
implementation.

DTGModule.cc	: C++ Implmentation of the DTGModule which encapsulates
		  the loading of a plugin. Used by the plugin test tool.
DTGModule.h	: C++ Class which encapsulates loading and using a plugin
		  Used by the plugin test tool.
dtg-utils.c	: C Implementation of the utility functions for the
		  data structures passed between the plugin and the Perforce
		  Defect Tracking Gateway system
dtg-utils.h	: Declarations of the utility functions for manipulating
		  the data structures passed between the plugin and
		  the Perforce Defect Tracking Gateway
README		: This file
